				<string>Works great for recipes, or any other list in text form. When reviewing recipes online, highlight the list of ingredients and in the Share Sheet use this shortcut to add each item as a reminders.

To use this shortcut from another app:
Highlight lines of text and tap the “Share…” option in the edit bar.
